https://www.artofmanliness.com/articles/the-prisoner-workout/

Use the value of the card to determine how many reps you do
Ace=13

Clubs: arms
Spades: legs
Diamonds: core
Hearts: cardio

clubs		biceps, triceps	(pushups, bicep curls, kettlebell)
Spades  	glutes, quads, hamstrings (squats, lunges)
hearts		cardio (jumping jack, burpees)
diamonds	abs (situps, plank)

- take 13 cards
- turn over 4 x 3 x 3 x 3 (13)
- every time you need to break during a set, add +1